      <section eId="sec_206_B">
        <num>206-B</num>
        <heading>Exemption of benefits payable under blanket accident insurance covering volunteer firefighters</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_206_B__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of section three thousand two hundred twelve of the\ninsurance law, but also any benefits payable or allowable under any such\npolicy or contract in the event of the death of an insured volunteer\nfirefighter shall be exempt from execution for the purpose of satisfying\nany debt or liability of the beneficiary designated in the policy or\ncontract, or in the event that the insured volunteer firefighter is a\nminor shall be exempt from execution for the purpose of satisfying any\ndebt or liability of the person to whom such benefits are payable\npursuant to subsection</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_206_B__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of section four thousand two hundred\nthirty-seven of the insurance law.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
